CARIN RTPBC Expanded Coverage Class Value Set

This value set adds concepts to the HL7-maintained coverage class value set related to discount coupons.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/coverage-class
  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin/CodeSystem/rtpbc-coupon-coverage-class
